      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs directly linked to clinical failure modes and regulatory submission acceptance criteria.",
      "rationale": "Construct stiffness governs load sharing with the vertebral column; yield force and force at 40 mm displacement are the regulatory acceptance metrics specified in ASTM F1717 and referenced in FDA guidance. All three QoIs directly relevant to the COU and the 510(k) submission decision. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
